{
  "texts": [
    "All must wear sackcloth and cry out earnestly to God.",
    "Turn from your evil ways and stop the violence you commit.",
    "Perhaps God will have mercy and relent from destroying us.\"",
    "9 When God saw their repentant hearts and that they had turned from their wickedness, He had compassion on them and did not bring upon them the destruction He had threatened.",
    "1 And the Lord spoke to Jonah a third time, saying, 2 \"Arise, go to Nineveh, the great city, and speak my words to them once more.\""
  ]
}